e white terror)<br />\n<br />\nBut the troops would withdraw after a while since the chairman Xi didn't want to hurt the reputation of autonomy and &quot;One Country, Two system.&quot; ,and Xi thought that Armed Army maybe caused fewer noise in worldwide than PLA.<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n請大家繼續堅持"},{"pid":"4a1d8f694cac2dde8edbb50c485f794ecc77380a","tid":1539094,"uid":21899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4f4a48a1307d190d2145104652e249454181c19","tid":1539094,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c09acd1dde297a9396ad457585d4d58d2aea336","tid":1539094,"uid":281263,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"有朋友話佢近幾集正常翻<br />\n但自從佢上次孖住廢陶叫人唔好嗌天琦口號，已經取消訂閱，一集都無睇再<br />\n底已露"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"佢嗰陣一直都係講你一係比個新meaning佢，唔係就比人對號入坐黎混淆視聽，根本屌嗰班人睇一半唔睇一半，一係就分化撚，而家佢自己都叫光復香港，而且的確黨媒都冇再屈港獨，佢地剩係尻up緊咩半獨立實體，黨媒自己都要吹噃高度自治"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"係 佢有講過話<br />\n<br />\n光復香港既自由同人權<br />\n革命香港民主制度，同舊時代區分<br />\n<br />\n大概係咁 唔知有無記錯"},{"pid":"0996fe705541b9bb6e3537b83b850a0c6bb15a89","tid":1539094,"uid":240372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"875d4981abcf71e74f2561ae35da6b005f071628","tid":1539094,"uid":31841,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:53:35.000Z","msg":"劉細良不嬲信唔過<br />\n係你班連登仔先吹奏佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:31:29.000Z","msg":"點解信唔過"},{"pid":"6f39c5189792e88ac15ed5e4599eee9399e673df","tid":1539094,"uid":247840,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:33:29.000Z","msg":"劉細良不嬲都係散水黨黨主席<br />\n<br />\n同埋維穩小隊隊目黎架啦"}]}